{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-05215/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-05215"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:52:15"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["high key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A bright camera flash goes off on a couple seated on a couch."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-05215","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-05215"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1/44b5e072-08c7-4d64-b8a8-68023a04a85c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T20:13:08.936Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The photographers’ flashbulbs wash out the characters, rendering them ghostly and confused in this tense moment. Despite Barbara Rose’s claim that she has brought “sincerity” to her relationship with Rubio Gurrerro, there is clearly a great deal of playacting going on.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:313.6772884269028,138.8796289844206,1214.1386632200886,728.1273079763664"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1/bf450aa4-08c1-430b-bc2d-734475fa2066","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T20:13:23.912Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This moment also comes from the press conference held before Barbara Hutton and Porfirio Rubirosa’s wedding: “The next question was directed at Rubirosa: ‘What is it that Barbara brought into your life?’ Rubi mumbled for a moment and then broke into French, saying that the word he wanted was ‘grand.’ Barbara raised an eyebrow at this response: ‘It was sincerity,’ she said. ‘I brought sincerity into his life’” (Haymann, <em>Poor Little Rich Girl</em>, 296). For a somewhat different account of this scene, see Shawn Levy’s <em>The Last Playboy</em> (203–205). A news reports on Hutton and Rubirosa’s wedding ceremony can be found <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW146896550 BCX0\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HbtpfDA26zY\"><u>here</u></a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW146896550 BCX0\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5gAoZKTZouM\"><u>here</u></a> and preparations for their honeymoon can be viewed <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW146896550 BCX0\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?si=_tyRnkKKyJEI4gyW&amp;v=uJCgCuiI5FI&amp;feature=youtu.be\"><u>here</u></a>.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05215/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:16.0037286041554,20.563528541289315,230.8437961595273,186.12213810930572"}}}]}]}]}